# Intelligent File Categorization System

This Python script automatically organizes files in a directory based on their content and name. Using advanced natural language processing via the OpenAI API, it analyzes each file, determines an appropriate category, and moves the file into a corresponding folder. The system supports various file types including text, PDF, Word documents, and images, making it a versatile tool for personal and professional file management.

Key Features:
- Automated file categorization using AI
- Support for multiple file formats
- OCR capabilities for image files
- Creation of category-based folders
- Easy-to-use single-directory operation

Ideal for users looking to streamline their file organization process with the power of AI.


## Instructions to use
just place this python script in the folder whose files you want to organize. Create your OpenAI api key and place it in a .env file in the same folder like this:

OPENAI_API_KEY='your-api-key-here'

Then run the program.

You can also modify it to take the folder path as input.